SUMMARY:[FREE] Prenatal Breastfeeding Workshop
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260324T180000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260324T200000
DTSTAMP:20260324T005607Z
UID:e2f9e38eb6b7dee818e601f53732e392@family-events-agent
SEQUENCE:0
CATEGORIES:children,play,toddler,museum,family
DESCRIPTION:Organizer: Pretend City Children's Museum - Events\\nCost: Fre
 e\\nDistance: 5.8 miles from home\\n\\nExpecting a little one soon?\nThis 
 class will teach you everything you need to know before\, during\, and aft
 er breastfeeding. Led by an International Board-Certified Lactation Consul
 tant (IBCLC) from MemorialCare Saddleback Medical Center\, this workshop c
 overs essential skills and real-life guidance to help you feel confident i
 n your feeding journey. Attendees will also have dedicated time to ask que
 stions and receive personalized support. \nFourth Tuesday of Every Month 
  \n6–8 PM\nCost: FREE\nREGISTER HERE\nThis is a child-free event.\nAbou
 t Play Partner MemorialCare Saddleback Medical Center&#8217\;s lactation
  team includes Registered Nurses who are also Internationally Board Certi
 fied Lactation Consultants (IBCLC). These lactation consultants support b
 reastfeeding moms both during their hospital stay and after they go home\,
  with follow-up visits in their outpatient clinic. They know that every mo
 m and baby are unique\, so they personalize care to help you have a succ
 essful and positive breastfeeding experience.\\n\\nMore info: https://www.
 pretendcity.org/events/prenatal-breastfeeding-workshop-2026-03-31/
LOCATION:Pretend City Children's Museum - Events\, 29 Hubble\, Irvine\, CA
 \, 92618
URL:https://www.pretendcity.org/events/prenatal-breastfeeding-workshop-202
 6-03-31/
BEGIN:VALARM
ACTION:DISPLAY
DESCRIPTION:Tomorrow: Prenatal Breastfeeding Workshop
TRIGGER:-P1D
END:VALARM
BEGIN:VALARM
ACTION:DISPLAY
DESCRIPTION:In 2 hours: Prenatal Breastfeeding Workshop
TRIGGER:-PT2H
END:VALARM
END:VEVENT
