DESCRIPTION:Organizer: Pretend City Children's Museum - Events\\nDistance:
  5.8 miles from home\\n\\nGet ready to rock\, roll\, sway\, sing\, and bop
 ! Because we’re bringing back Kidstock Music &amp\; Arts Festival! Enjoy
  live musical performances throughout the week and explore a mix of musica
 l styles! Because of your generosity during Igniting Potential\, Kidstock 
 will be bigger\, brighter\, and more hands-on than ever!\n3/31\n\n11 am: T
 he Rhythm Child Network\n2:30 pm: Pacific Dance\n\n\n4/1\n\n11 am: Ashley 
 Mills Monaghan\n2:30 pm: Jukie Davie\n\n\n4/2\n\n11 am &amp\; 2:30 pm Drum
 atiX\n\n\n4/3\n\n11 am: Conga Kids\n2:30 pm: Philharmonic Society’s Oran
 ge County Youth Symphony musicians\n\n\n4/4\n\n11 am: SoCal Drum Party\n1 
 pm: Bhangra by Nature\n2:30 pm: El Centro Cultural de México\n\n4/5 CLOSE
 D for Easter\nWeek 2\n4/7\n\n11 am &amp\; 2:30 pm Fouta Toro West African 
 Dance and Drum Ensemble\n\n4/8\n\n11 am: Backhaus Dance\n2:30 pm: Mommy Ce
 nter Music\n\n4/9\n\n11 am: WeBreak Hip-Hop Dance Company\n2:30 pm: Ufirst
  Artist\n\n4/10\n\n11 am &amp\; 2:30 pm: Platinum Performing Arts\n\n4/11\
 n\n11 am: El Centro Cultural de México\n1 pm: The Portobellas\n2:30 pm: K
 ymberly Stewart\n\n*Events and dates are subject to change.\nThis exhibit 
 is included in museum admission. Space is limited! Book your tickets no
 w. \nEvent DetailsMarch 31 – April 11Performance times vary by daySprin
 g Break hours: Tuesday–Sunday\, 10 am–4 pmClosed April 5 for EasterEve
 nts subject to change.\nFAQs\nIs Kidstock included with admission?Yes. All
  performances are included with regular museum admission.\nWhat ages is Ki
 dstock best for?The festival is designed for children ages 0–8 and thei
 r families.\nDo performances happen every day?Yes. Live music or dance per
 formances take place daily during the festival\, except when the museum is
  closed.\\n\\nMore info: https://www.pretendcity.org/events/kidstock-2/
LOCATION:Pretend City Children's Museum - Events\, 29 Hubble\, Irvine\, CA
 \, 92618
URL:https://www.pretendcity.org/events/kidstock-2/
