BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:We Read Wednesdays with Empowering Readers OC
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260415T110000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260415T120000
DTSTAMP:20260324T005607Z
UID:1ef55b80c01657b5b787673aabf4e099@family-events-agent
SEQUENCE:0
CATEGORIES:children,play,toddler,museum,family
DESCRIPTION:Organizer: Pretend City Children's Museum - Events\\nDistance:
  5.8 miles from home\\n\\nPretend City Children’s Museum and Parentis Fo
 undation are partnering for something truly magical at We Read Wednesdays
 \, where Littles and Grans read together! Our wonderful Empowering Reade
 rs OC reading mentors are bringing the joy of storytelling into the playfu
 l world of Pretend City\, where imagination comes alive and every corner i
 nvites discovery.\nThis partnership is so important because it introduces 
 children to the love of books in a way that feels fun\, welcoming\, and sh
 ared. When young learners and older adult mentors gather in a place built 
 for wonder\, stories become more than words on a page. They become moments
  of connection\, confidence\, and inspiration across generations.\nTogethe
 r\, Pretend City and Empowering Readers OC are creating a community where 
 reading is joyful and every story sparks a love of reading.\n\nTIME: 11am
  &#8211\; 12pm\nAbout the Play Partner:\nEmpowering Readers OC\, a program
  of Parentis Foundation\, provides evidence-based literacy intervention an
 d intergenerational mentoring to students in grades 1–5 who are reading 
 below grade level. By pairing trained older adult volunteers with students
 \, the program builds strong reading skills\, confidence\, and a foundatio
 n for lifelong learning.\\n\\nMore info: https://www.pretendcity.org/event
 s/we-read-wednesdays-with-empowering-readers-oc/
LOCATION:Pretend City Children's Museum - Events\, 29 Hubble\, Irvine\, CA
 \, 92618
URL:https://www.pretendcity.org/events/we-read-wednesdays-with-empowering-
 readers-oc/
BEGIN:VALARM
ACTION:DISPLAY
DESCRIPTION:Tomorrow: We Read Wednesdays with Empowering Readers OC
TRIGGER:-P1D
END:VALARM
