UID:6ef80b77898452b2865f46a2f8fd7fe9@family-events-agent
SEQUENCE:0
CATEGORIES:children,play,toddler,museum,family
DESCRIPTION:Organizer: Pretend City Children's Museum - Events\\nCost: Fre
 e\\nDistance: 5.8 miles from home\\n\\nPretend City Children’s Museum Go
 od To Go Fair: A FREE Family-Friendly Event! This FREE event is perfect fo
 r families with children ages 0-5. Enjoy a variety of activities\, resourc
 es\, and services designed to support your child’s development and overa
 ll well-being.\nTIME: 9 am-1 pm\nPretend City Parking Lot\nRain or Shine\n
 \nDevelopmental Screenings:\n⦁ Check your child’s developmental milest
 ones and receive valuable insights into their growth\n⦁ Vision Screening
 s: Detect early signs of vision issues to ensure your child’s eyes are h
 ealthy.\n⦁ Dental Screenings: Keep your child’s smile bright and healt
 hy with a free dental check-up.\n⦁ Social-Emotional Screenings: Assess 
 your child’s emotional well-being and get support for their mental healt
 h.\n⦁ And more!\nWhy Attend?\nEarly Detection: Catch potential health co
 ncerns early\, allowing for timely intervention and support.\nFree Service
 s: Access these important health screenings at no cost to you.\nExpert Gui
 dance: Receive advice and resources from trained professionals to support 
 your child’s development and health.\nPLUS\, your child can earn a FREE 
 ticket to Pretend City by completing 3 Health screenings!\nDon’t miss th
 e chance to connect with incredible organizations!\nOur Sponsors: CalOptim
 a Health\, Fairmont Schools\, Hoag\, Orange County Department of Education
 \, PNC Bank\n*The event is free\; please note admission to the museum is n
 ot included.\\n\\nMore info: https://www.pretendcity.org/events/good-to-go
 -fair-2/
LOCATION:Pretend City Children's Museum - Events\, 29 Hubble\, Irvine\, CA
 \, 92618
URL:https://www.pretendcity.org/events/good-to-go-fair-2/
