SUMMARY:Earth Day in the City
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260422T110000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260422T110000
DTSTAMP:20260324T005607Z
UID:bfaf267575916753785c3144491ff99e@family-events-agent
SEQUENCE:0
CATEGORIES:children,play,toddler,museum,family
DESCRIPTION:Organizer: Pretend City Children's Museum - Events\\nDistance:
  5.8 miles from home\\n\\nCelebrate Earth Day at Pretend City with activit
 ies that help children learn how to care for our planet. Families are invi
 ted to explore simple\, hands-on experiences that highlight nature\, conse
 rvation\, and everyday ways we can all help protect the Earth. \n\nTIMES:
  11 AM &amp\; 2:30 PM\n\n*Members do not require a reservation.\n*Events a
 nd dates are subject to change.\n\nAbout the play partner:\n\nOC Waste &am
 p\; Recycling serves the County’s solid waste disposal needs by providin
 g waste management services\, operating public landfills\, protecting the 
 local environment\, investing in renewable energy enterprises and promot
 ing recycling in order to ensure a safe and healthy community for curren
 t and future generations. OCWR also provides education\, outreach\, and su
 stainability programs that help residents reduce waste and support state a
 nd local mandates.\\n\\nMore info: https://www.pretendcity.org/events/eart
 h-day-in-the-city/
LOCATION:Pretend City Children's Museum - Events\, 29 Hubble\, Irvine\, CA
 \, 92618
URL:https://www.pretendcity.org/events/earth-day-in-the-city/
